name: Godot's Voyage
description:
**A submission for Mini Jam 24: Space**

Navigate your rocket, return safely to the space station. Because it's tea time and they have cream puff today!

Everything was built in less than 24 hours total, from learning Godot for the first time and building this 3 short levels game.

Credits

BGM: amenemone

Programming: juunishi master

Art: Kenney Asset
